name: KITSUNE
description:
Kitsune udon is my favorite type of udon. I'm always order more inari for my udon.
Inari is the Shinto deity of rice. Originally, kitsune were Inari's messengers, but the line between the two is now blurred so that Inari Ōkami may be depicted as a fox.
- 
Got a new tool, and now it's my time to join Bwople x Monday Art Club Art Contest.
